PrecisOrder which provides for (a) the WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL of those lands identified as "NORTH BAFFIN", "KEEWATIN" and "BYLOT ISLAND" WITHDRAWAL AREAS, as well as specified subsurface areas, in order to facilitate the settlement of land claims made by the Tungavik Federation of Nunavut (TFN), and (b) the revocation of a previous Order in Council having much the same effect (P.C. 1991-932).
